               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsān maḥyawi “The Life-Giving Homily” (fols. 3ra) &#xD; I-1)
                     Introductory prayer (fol.3ra-va) &#xD; I-2) Reading for Monday, Compline
                     (nǝwam) (fols. 3va-18ra) &#xD; I-3) Reading for Tuesday, Matins (manfaqa lelit)
                     (fols.18ra-31vb) &#xD; I-4) Reading for Wednesday, Lauds (nagh) (fols.
                     31vb-42rb) &#xD; I-5) Reading for Thursday, Terce (śalastu säʿat) (fols.
                     42rb-55rb) &#xD; I-6) Reading for Friday, Sext (qätr) (fols. 55rb-67va)&#xD;
                     I-7) Reading for Saturday, None (täsaʿtu säʿat) (fols. 67va-79va)&#xD; I-8)
                     Reading for Sunday, Vespers (śark) (fols. 79va-94va)&#xD; II) Malkǝʾa madḫane
                     ʿālam “Image of the Saviour of the World” (fols. 94vb-100rb).</summary>
